%% Standard request lifecycle (linear + optional branches)

flowchart TD
  A[User action] --> B[React component]
  B --> C[API route]
  C --> D[Auth check]
  D --> E[Tenant resolution]
  E --> F[Validator]
  F --> G[Module service]
  G --> H[Prisma query]
  H --> I[Domain event optional]
  I --> J[Notification trigger]
  J --> K[HTTP response]
  K --> L[UI refresh]

  G -.->|optional| Q[Action queue item]
  C -.->|optional| M[Analytics tracking]
  D -.->|optional| L2[Structured logging]

  style Q stroke-dasharray: 5 5
  style M stroke-dasharray: 5 5
  style L2 stroke-dasharray: 5 5
